{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.1","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 10:1","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.009.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.010.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Outrage fait par le roi des Ammonites aux serviteurs de David. \u2014 Guerre contre les Ammonites et leurs alli\u00e9s<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-19: cf. 1 Ch 19. Ps 20; 21; 2:8-12; 46:8-10.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.10.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>\n    Apr\u00e8s cela, le roi des fils d\u2019Ammon mourut, et Hanun, son fils, r\u00e9gna \u00e0 sa place.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10","name":"2 Samuel 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10.2","name":"2 Samuel 10:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.9.13","name":"2 Samuel 9:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.2","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 10:2","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.010.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.010.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.10.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>David dit: Je montrerai de la bienveillance \u00e0 Hanun, fils de Nachasch, comme son p\u00e8re en a montr\u00e9 \u00e0 mon \u00e9gard. Et David envoya ses serviteurs pour le consoler au sujet de son p\u00e8re. Lorsque les serviteurs de David arriv\u00e8rent dans le pays des fils d\u2019Ammon,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10","name":"2 Samuel 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10.3","name":"2 Samuel 10:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10.1","name":"2 Samuel 10:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.3","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 10:3","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.010.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.010.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.10.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>les chefs des fils d\u2019Ammon dirent \u00e0 Hanun, leur ma\u00eetre: Penses-tu que ce soit pour honorer ton p\u00e8re que David t\u2019envoie des consolateurs? N\u2019est-ce pas pour reconna\u00eetre et explorer la ville, et pour la d\u00e9truire, qu\u2019il envoie ses serviteurs aupr\u00e8s de toi?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10","name":"2 Samuel 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10.4","name":"2 Samuel 10:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10.2","name":"2 Samuel 10:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.4","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 10:4","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.010.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.010.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.10.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Alors Hanun saisit les serviteurs de David, leur fit raser la moiti\u00e9 de la barbe, et fit couper leurs habits par le milieu jusqu\u2019au haut des cuisses. Puis il les cong\u00e9dia.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10","name":"2 Samuel 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10.5","name":"2 Samuel 10:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10.3","name":"2 Samuel 10:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.5","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 10:5","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.010.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.010.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.10.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>David, qui fut inform\u00e9, envoya des gens \u00e0 leur rencontre, car ces hommes \u00e9taient dans une grande confusion; et le roi leur fit dire: Restez \u00e0 J\u00e9richo jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce que votre barbe ait repouss\u00e9, et revenez ensuite.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10","name":"2 Samuel 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10.6","name":"2 Samuel 10:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10.4","name":"2 Samuel 10:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.6","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 10:6","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.010.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.010.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.10.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Les fils d\u2019Ammon, voyant qu\u2019ils s\u2019\u00e9taient rendus odieux \u00e0 David, firent enr\u00f4ler \u00e0 leur solde vingt mille hommes de pied chez les Syriens de Beth-Rehob et chez les Syriens de Tsoba, mille hommes chez le roi de Maaca, et douze mille hommes chez les gens de Tob.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10","name":"2 Samuel 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10.7","name":"2 Samuel 10:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10.5","name":"2 Samuel 10:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.7","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 10:7","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.010.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.010.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.10.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>A cette nouvelle, David envoya contre eux Joab et toute l\u2019arm\u00e9e, les hommes vaillants.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10","name":"2 Samuel 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10.8","name":"2 Samuel 10:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10.6","name":"2 Samuel 10:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.8","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 10:8","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.010.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.010.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.10.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Les fils d\u2019Ammon sortirent, et se rang\u00e8rent en bataille \u00e0 l\u2019entr\u00e9e de la porte; les Syriens de Tsoba et de Rehob, et les hommes de Tob et de Maaca, \u00e9taient \u00e0 part dans la campagne.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10","name":"2 Samuel 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10.9","name":"2 Samuel 10:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10.7","name":"2 Samuel 10:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.9","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 10:9","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.010.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.010.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.10.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Joab vit qu\u2019il avait \u00e0 combattre par devant et par derri\u00e8re. Il choisit alors sur toute l\u2019\u00e9lite d\u2019Isra\u00ebl un corps, qu\u2019il opposa aux Syriens;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10","name":"2 Samuel 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10.10","name":"2 Samuel 10:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10.8","name":"2 Samuel 10:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.10","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 10:10","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.010.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.010.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.10.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>et il pla\u00e7a sous le commandement de son fr\u00e8re Abischa\u00ef le reste du peuple, pour faire face aux fils d\u2019Ammon.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10","name":"2 Samuel 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10.11","name":"2 Samuel 10:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10.9","name":"2 Samuel 10:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.11","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 10:11","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.010.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.010.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.10.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Il dit: Si les Syriens sont plus forts que moi, tu viendras \u00e0 mon secours; et si les fils d\u2019Ammon sont plus forts que toi, j\u2019irai te secourir.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10","name":"2 Samuel 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10.12","name":"2 Samuel 10:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10.10","name":"2 Samuel 10:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.12","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 10:12","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.010.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.010.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.10.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Sois ferme, et montrons du courage pour notre peuple et pour les villes de notre Dieu, et que l\u2019\u00c9ternel fasse ce qui lui semblera bon!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10","name":"2 Samuel 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10.13","name":"2 Samuel 10:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10.11","name":"2 Samuel 10:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.13","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 10:13","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.010.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.010.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.10.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Joab, avec son peuple, s\u2019avan\u00e7a pour attaquer les Syriens, et ils s\u2019enfuirent devant lui.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10","name":"2 Samuel 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10.14","name":"2 Samuel 10:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10.12","name":"2 Samuel 10:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.14","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 10:14","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.010.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.010.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.10.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Et quand les fils d\u2019Ammon virent que les Syriens avaient pris la fuite, ils s\u2019enfuirent aussi devant Abischa\u00ef et rentr\u00e8rent dans la ville. Joab s\u2019\u00e9loigna des fils d\u2019Ammon et revint \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10","name":"2 Samuel 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10.15","name":"2 Samuel 10:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10.13","name":"2 Samuel 10:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.15","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 10:15","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.010.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.010.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.10.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Les Syriens, voyant qu\u2019ils avaient \u00e9t\u00e9 battus par Isra\u00ebl, r\u00e9unirent leurs forces.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10","name":"2 Samuel 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10.16","name":"2 Samuel 10:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10.14","name":"2 Samuel 10:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.16","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 10:16","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.010.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.010.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.10.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Hadar\u00e9zer envoya chercher les Syriens qui \u00e9taient de l\u2019autre c\u00f4t\u00e9 du fleuve; et ils arriv\u00e8rent \u00e0 H\u00e9lam, ayant \u00e0 leur t\u00eate Schobac, chef de l\u2019arm\u00e9e d\u2019Hadar\u00e9zer.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10","name":"2 Samuel 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10.17","name":"2 Samuel 10:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10.15","name":"2 Samuel 10:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.17","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 10:17","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.010.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.010.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.10.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>On l\u2019annon\u00e7a \u00e0 David, qui assembla tout Isra\u00ebl, passa le Jourdain, et vint \u00e0 H\u00e9lam. Les Syriens se pr\u00e9par\u00e8rent \u00e0 la rencontre de David, et lui livr\u00e8rent bataille.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10","name":"2 Samuel 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10.18","name":"2 Samuel 10:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10.16","name":"2 Samuel 10:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.18","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 10:18","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.010.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.010.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.10.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Mais les Syriens s\u2019enfuirent devant Isra\u00ebl. Et David leur tua les troupes de sept cents chars et quarante mille cavaliers; il frappa aussi le chef de leur arm\u00e9e, Schobac, qui mourut sur place.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10","name":"2 Samuel 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10.19","name":"2 Samuel 10:19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10.17","name":"2 Samuel 10:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.19","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 10:19","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.010.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.011.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.10.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Tous les rois soumis \u00e0 Hadar\u00e9zer, se voyant battus par Isra\u00ebl, firent la paix avec Isra\u00ebl et lui furent assujettis. Et les Syriens n\u2019os\u00e8rent plus secourir les fils d\u2019Ammon.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10","name":"2 Samuel 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.11.1","name":"2 Samuel 11:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.11.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10.18","name":"2 Samuel 10:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb554b069.87475272');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb554b069.87475272\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb554b069.87475272","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb554b069.87475272'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb554b069.87475272\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}